---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Contact | Cranes Consulting Tampa"
  description="Book a 30-minute fit call with Cranes Consulting. Lean Six Sigma and program management for Tampa Bay small businesses."
>
  <section class="border-b border-navy-100">
    <div class="container-x py-20 md:py-24">
      <span class="eyebrow">Contact</span>
      <h1 class="mt-6 max-w-4xl text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[56px] font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-balance leading-[1.05] text-navy-900">
        30 minutes. No deck. Just the real problem.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">
        Bring a real problem. A margin leak, a shelfware system, a stuck program, a grant deadline. I'll bring ten years of federal-scale program discipline and a Lean Six Sigma playbook. If there's a fit, we'll talk scope. If not, you'll leave with two or three ideas you can run with on your own.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-x py-20 md:py-24 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
    <div class="lg:col-span-7">
      <ContactForm />
    </div>

    <aside class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-8">
      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-amber-600">Direct</p>
        <p class="mt-3 font-bold text-navy-800">Tyler Alexander</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-mute">Founder, Cranes Consulting</p>
        <div class="mt-5 space-y-3">
          <a href="mailto:tyler@cranesconsultingfl.com" class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-navy-800 hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors">
            <span class="h-9 w-9 rounded-lg bg-navy-50 text-navy-700 grid place-items-center">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="m3 7 9 6 9-6"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="font-medium">tyler@cranesconsultingfl.com</span>
          </a>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-ink-soft">
            <span class="h-9 w-9 rounded-lg bg-navy-50 text-navy-700 grid place-items-center">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span>Tampa, FL · Serving Tampa Bay &amp; Central Florida</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-amber-600">What to expect</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm text-ink-soft">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="shrink-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-navy-800 text-white grid place-items-center text-xs font-bold">1</span>
            <span><strong class="text-navy-800">Reply within one business day,</strong> usually same day.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="shrink-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-navy-800 text-white grid place-items-center text-xs font-bold">2</span>
            <span><strong class="text-navy-800">A 30-minute call.</strong> No deck, no pitch. Tell me what's going on.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="shrink-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-navy-800 text-white grid place-items-center text-xs font-bold">3</span>
            <span><strong class="text-navy-800">Proposal inside 48 hours</strong> if there's a fit. Fixed fee, clear deliverables.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="shrink-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-navy-800 text-white grid place-items-center text-xs font-bold">4</span>
            <span><strong class="text-navy-800">Kickoff inside 2 weeks</strong> from signed engagement.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 p-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-amber-700">Hurricane recovery</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-navy-800 leading-relaxed">
          If you're navigating Helene / Milton rebuild funds (Rebuilding for Tomorrow, CDBG-DR, FEMA PA), mention it in your message. We prioritize those inquiries.
        </p>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </section>
</Base>
